Package jsx.ui.vect.canvas

For extra vector graphic widgets for interactive drawing based on 2d-canvas.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CanvasDraft An abstract base class for drawing tools that can interactively draw on a wrapped canvas with the help of a cached draft canvas.
CanvasDraw An abstract base class for drawing tools that can interactively draw on a wrapped canvas.
CanvasLine Defines a drawing wrapper that interactively draws lines on a wrapped canvas with the help of a cached draft canvas.
CanvasPaint Defines a drawing wrapper that interactively paints on the wrapped canvas.
CanvasSketch Defines a drawing wrapper that interactively sketches on the wrapped canvas.
 

Package jsx.ui.vect.canvas Description

For extra vector graphic widgets for interactive drawing based on 2d-canvas.
